# Google Calendar OAuth
# How to set up:
# 1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/
# 2. Create a new project or select existing one
# 3. Enable Google Calendar API (APIs & Services > Library)
# 4. Create OAuth 2.0 Client ID (APIs & Services > Credentials)
#    - Application type: Web application
#    - Add Authorized redirect URIs: https://yourdomain.vercel.app/api/google/callback
#                                    http://localhost:3000/api/google/callback (for development)
# 5. Copy Client ID and Client Secret to these environment variables
